  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.25.1",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:1",
      "text": "David and the chiefs of the service also set apart for the service certain of the sons of Asaph, and of Heman, and of Jeduthun, who should prophesy with lyres, with harps, and with cymbals. The list of those who did the work and of their duties was:",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.25.2",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:2",
      "text": "Of the sons of Asaph: Zaccur, Joseph, Nethaniah, and Asharelah, sons of Asaph, under the direction of Asaph, who prophesied under the direction of the king.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.25.3",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:3",
      "text": "Of Jeduthun, the sons of Jeduthun: Gedaliah, Zeri, Jeshaiah, Shime-i, Hashabiah, and Mattithiah, six, under the direction of their father Jeduthun, who prophesied with the lyre in thanksgiving and praise to the Lord.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.25.4",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:4",
      "text": "Of Heman, the sons of Heman: Bukkiah, Mattaniah, Uzziel, Shebuel, and Jerimoth, Hananiah, Hanani, Eliathah, Giddalti, and Romamti-ezer, Joshbekashah, Mallothi, Hothir, Mahazi-oth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.25.5",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:5",
      "text": "All these were the sons of Heman the king's seer, according to the promise of God to exalt him; for God had given Heman fourteen sons and three daughters.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.25.6",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:6",
      "text": "They were all under the direction of their father in the music in the house of the Lord with cymbals, harps, and lyres for the service of the house of God. Asaph, Jeduthun, and Heman were under the order of the king.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.25.7",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:7",
      "text": "The number of them along with their brethren, who were trained in singing to the Lord, all who were skilful, was two hundred and eighty-eight.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.25.8",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:8",
      "text": "And they cast lots for their duties, small and great, teacher and pupil alike.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.25.9",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:9",
      "text": "The first lot fell for Asaph to Joseph; the second to Gedaliah, to him and his brethren and his sons, twelve;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.25.10",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:10",
      "text": "the third to Zaccur, his sons and his brethren, twelve;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
